== The Kid Report

This application was built to help teachers communicate with parents.  It is opensource.  Developers - if you have kids and need a tool for your class or school, you are welcome to use the kid report and add features that you may need.


== What is it?

It's a simple cms tool, with some more-powerful messaging tools.  This allows the teacher to create pages, messages, upload documents, and create a schedule.


== Adding features

If you find that you would like to add features to The Kid Report, simply send a pull request.


== Features wanted

Tests, always
Switch from prototype to jquery
Add SMS support


